  "update_count": 39,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIf user accepts a virtual credit card suggestion for autofill, ChromeAutofillClient::OnVirtualCardDataAvailable is called after the credit card info was fetched. On android platform, it then calls AutofillSnackbarControllerImpl::Show to show the virtual card snackbar [1]"
